            Your <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">Link-in-Bio</span>,<br>
            Beautifully Simple
          <% } %>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary mb-8" style="max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
          <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
            Your Velink profile is ready! Manage your links, track analytics, and share your unique page with the world.
          <% } else { %>
            Create a stunning landing page for all your links. Share your content, grow your audience, and track your success with advanced analytics.
          <% } %>
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
          <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
            <% if (typeof username !== 'undefined' && username) { %>
              <a href="/profile/<%= username %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="bi bi-eye"></i>
                View Your Profile
              </a>
            <% } %>
            <a href="/manage" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
              <i class="bi bi-gear"></i>
              Manage Links
            </a>
          <% } else { %>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
              <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff"></i>
